docs.text: Welcome to DJ Bot Support DJ Bot is a multifunctional bot with several commands sorted into several categories. It is optimized the best it can be in order to bring the best experience for users. Soo what are you waiting for? Go try it out! Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. DJ Bot test...press start
